FBIS3-49420 "dreeu007_b_94004" FBIS-EEU-94-007 Document Type:Daily Report 11 Jan 1994 BULGARIA Deputy Defense Ministers, Ambassador Appointed AU1101144094 Sofia BULGARSKA ARMIYA in Bulgarian 6 Jan 94 p 1 AU1101144094 Sofia BULGARSKA ARMIYA Language: Bulgarian Article Type:BFN [Unattributed report: "Personnel Changes in Defense Ministry"] [Text] By a presidential decree Mr. Mikhail Atanasov Srebrev has been released from the post of deputy minister of defense on military-political issues, because of his appointment as Bulgarian ambassador to Austria. Boyko Nikolov Noev has been appointed to the post of deputy defense minister on military-political issues. Vladimir Trifonov Penchev has been appointed deputy defense minister on financial and foreign currency issues.
